  "text": "Finally, this approach increases burdens on the proxy server. If the proxy server is overloaded it could adversely affect the web browsing performance [CITATION_1] . Because the proxy is in charge of fetching web objects and rendering web pages on behalf of its clients, the computation load to the proxy is much heavier than the load on conventional web proxy servers.",
