      "title": "War of the mobile browsers",
      "abstract": "Wireless applications for mobile Web browsers can enrich user experience beyond the desktop environment. Server-transcoding and client rendering enable the wireless Web, while open platforms give applications developers extensions to expand mobile software's future."
